title = "Roasted Broccoli"

[ingredients]
1 1/4 lbs; broccoli crowns
2 1/2 Tbsp; olive oil
1 clove; garlic
; salt & pepper

[instructions]
Preheat oven to 400ºF.
Line a baking sheet with aluminum foil. Spray foil with non-stick cooking spray.
Toss broccoli crowns in bowl with olive oil, garlic, sal & pepper to evenly coat.
Spread across sheet pan evenly and roast for 12-15 minutes at 400ºF
